    <p><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l7' data-llen='153:179'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0052', 'WYG', '001-1a' );" name="001-1a" class="pb">[001-1a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l8' data-llen='179:187'>欽定四庫全書</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l9' data-llen='187:194'>　詩札卷一</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l10' data-llen='194:215'>　　　　　　　　　　翰林院檢討毛竒齡撰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l11' data-llen='215:238'>予既依汝南太守聽寫官言詩削牘去之然猶未達也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l12' data-llen='238:261'>往以札問訊遂有徵諸咫尺者續續為記曰詩札雖然</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l13' data-llen='261:282'>此非言詩之為箋也特不可忘矣走者官自稱耳</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l14' data-llen='282:305'>謹奉敎鄉但解毛萇作毛傳從來亦如是此否耳魯人</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l15' data-llen='305:328'>大毛公毛享作故訓傳授之趙人小毛公萇既而河間</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l16' data-llen='328:354'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0052', 'WYG', '001-1b' );" name="001-1b" class="pb">[001-1b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l17' data-llen='354:377'>獻王得以獻之始以萇為博士則是毛享作毛傳詎萇</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l18' data-llen='377:383'>作耳主臣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l19' data-llen='383:406'>謹奉教鄉疑小序何人作有為孔子有為卜子有為衞</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l20' data-llen='406:429'>宏有為國史走臆通是毛享作何以知之按漢志毛詩</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l21' data-llen='429:452'>二十九卷故訓傳三十卷鄭氏詩譜有云大毛為故訓</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l22' data-llen='452:475'>傳今毛詩比卷卷首有若篇詁訓傳若干文按之故即</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l23' data-llen='475:499'>序首一句也第不連屬篇題于篇題下判云若干章章若</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l24' data-llen='499:522'>干句然後入此一句假如闗雎詩必先曰闗雎三章一</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l25' data-llen='522:548'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0052', 'WYG', '001-2a' );" name="001-2a" class="pb">[001-2a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l26' data-llen='548:571'>章章四句二章章八句然後曰后妃之德也此是故也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l27' data-llen='571:594'>何以知之以關雎詩篇題下知之關雎五章章四句此</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l28' data-llen='594:618'>是鄭𤣥更定章句又云故言三章一章章四句二章章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l29' data-llen='618:642'>八句則此故言是故也篇題下凡鄭𤣥有所更定輙加</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l30' data-llen='642:665'>故言判之而孔氏正義于序下分疏必曰若句至若句</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l31' data-llen='665:688'>獨關雎以毛鄭不同故不疏而葛覃序下即疏云葛覃</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l32' data-llen='688:711'>三章章六句至以婦道則當時序首篇題下必皆有章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l33' data-llen='711:734'>句若干等字而後人乃削去之矣故知序首一句連章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l34' data-llen='734:760'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0052', 'WYG', '001-2b' );" name="001-2b" class="pb">[001-2b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l35' data-llen='760:783'>句是故也自序首一句後便是訓如關雎序后妃之德</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l36' data-llen='783:806'>也一句是故風之始也至末便是訓訓者推訓此一句</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l37' data-llen='806:829'>耳然與首句不甚合若二人作自關雎詩文下興也以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l38' data-llen='829:852'>後則是傳傳者傳詩文也然又與故訓不必合又若二</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l39' data-llen='852:876'>人作則臆故之為㫖故有此語而今述之也非謂詁也訓</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l40' data-llen='876:900'>者訓此故則可不合傳詩文又非訓此故也則又可不合</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l41' data-llen='900:923'>此可知耳然則稱毛故訓傳即毛序訓傳此明甚著者</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l42' data-llen='923:927'>主臣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l43' data-llen='927:953'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0052', 'WYG', '001-3a' );" name="001-3a" class="pb">[001-3a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l44' data-llen='953:976'>謹奉教二南即是風或但稱南此是樂名耳如禮稱胥</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l45' data-llen='976:999'>鼓南左傳稱見舞象箾南籥者即詩亦云以雅以南此</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l46' data-llen='999:1022'>畢樂部名非詩名也或又謂即稱風又稱南必南不名</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l47' data-llen='1022:1045'>風此不然樂記曰正直而靜廉而謙者宜歌風溫良而</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l48' data-llen='1045:1068'>能斷者宜歌齊既稱風又稱齊詎齊亦不得名風邪主</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l49' data-llen='1068:1071'>臣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l50' data-llen='1071:1094'>謹奉教程大昌曰詩有南無國風古無稱國風者即弼</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l51' data-llen='1094:1117'>鄘以下亦不得稱國風此否也表記曰國風曰我躬不</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l52' data-llen='1117:1143'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0052', 'WYG', '001-3b' );" name="001-3b" class="pb">[001-3b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l53' data-llen='1143:1166'>閱皇恤我後國風曰心之憂矣於我歸説此不稱國風</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l54' data-llen='1166:1172'>而何主臣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l55' data-llen='1172:1195'>謹奉教南以周召之化自北而南為二南固然然又有</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l56' data-llen='1195:1218'>二㫖此固不必然然記異耳呂覽云塗山之女令其妾</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l57' data-llen='1218:1241'>待禹于塗山之陽女乃作歌曰候人兮猗實為南音周</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l58' data-llen='1241:1264'>公召公取以為周南召南則以周之二南原本南音謂</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l59' data-llen='1264:1287'>古早有所稱南者此則以南為古之樂名然耳又逸周</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l60' data-llen='1287:1310'>書稱南國名南氏有二臣力鈞勢醜競進爭權君勿能</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l61' data-llen='1310:1336'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0052', 'WYG', '001-4a' );" name="001-4a" class="pb">[001-4a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l62' data-llen='1336:1359'>制南氏用分為二南之國而水經註又云據韓嬰序詩</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l63' data-llen='1359:1382'>其地在南郡南陽之間則以此二南國為詩之二南故</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l64' data-llen='1382:1398'>引韓嬰序詩為驗則南國名耳主臣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l65' data-llen='1398:1421'>謹奉教荇菜為接予或作菨予云比之后妃言德行如</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l66' data-llen='1421:1444'>此可以妾餘草矣此是埤雅引王文公說也此底解或</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l67' data-llen='1444:1467'>云漢皇后位下有偼伃名即接予音並同古之命此名</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l68' data-llen='1467:1481'>或亦取此但此未可據者主臣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l69' data-llen='1481:1504'>謹奉教左右芼之芼字鄉但解作採擇獨朱子曰熟而</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l70' data-llen='1504:1530'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0052', 'WYG', '001-4b' );" name="001-4b" class="pb">[001-4b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l71' data-llen='1530:1553'>薦之按禮凡蔬茹煮於湇者皆謂芼若昬禮芼之以蘋</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l72' data-llen='1553:1576'>藻内則□酏酒醴芼羮又云雉兎皆有芼又儀禮饋食</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l73' data-llen='1576:1599'>皆有鉶芼朱子云是也特朱子語類又記魏才仲問芼</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l74' data-llen='1599:1613'>㫖答曰是採擇㫖又不同主臣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l75' data-llen='1613:1636'>謹奉教是刈是濩濩韓詩云瀹也若孫炎云謂煮之於</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l76' data-llen='1636:1658'>鑊則是以濩為鑊也今按爾雅郭註直作鑊字主臣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l77' data-llen='1658:1681'>謹奉教甘棠之憩偶爾爾鄭以為重煩勞百姓此固矣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l78' data-llen='1681:1704'>但韓詩外傳云昔者周道之盛召伯在朝有司請營召</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l79' data-llen='1704:1730'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0052', 'WYG', '001-5a' );" name="001-5a" class="pb">[001-5a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l80' data-llen='1730:1753'>以居召伯曰嗟矣以吾一身而勞民此非吾先君文王</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l81' data-llen='1753:1776'>之志也于是出就蒸庶于阡陌之間暴去曠野屋于樹</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l82' data-llen='1776:1799'>下又說苑云召公述職當蠶桑之時不欲變民功故不</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l83' data-llen='1799:1822'>入邑中舍處甘棠之下而聽訟焉以二說觀之皆謂是</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l84' data-llen='1822:1845'>慮煩百姓故去棠下然則鄭氏之㫖亦鄉有是者主臣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l85' data-llen='1845:1868'>謹奉教婉如清揚詎婉而似清揚也如即而矣春秋星</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l86' data-llen='1868:1891'>隕如雨是星隕而雨樂府艾如張是艾而張或曰是倒</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l87' data-llen='1891:1900'>句清揚婉如主臣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l88' data-llen='1900:1926'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0052', 'WYG', '001-5b' );" name="001-5b" class="pb">[001-5b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l89' data-llen='1926:1949'>謹奉教摽有梅傾筐墍之塈說文訓塗尚書曰惟其塗</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l90' data-llen='1949:1972'>墍茨信然即與摽取㫖何與矣此應從吕氏讀詩記作</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l91' data-llen='1972:1993'>曁暨訓為及自此而傾筐及之矣是落盡耳主臣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l92' data-llen='1993:2016'>謹奉教蝃蝀詩不知命也凡命字有四訓毛鄭通云不</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l93' data-llen='2016:2039'>待父母之命此告命之㫖耳程子曰命正理也以道制</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l94' data-llen='2039:2062'>欲則能順命此性命之㫖耳蘓子由曰人茍知事之有</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l95' data-llen='2062:2085'>命也則不為不義安而俟之矣此時命之㫖耳若韓詩</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l96' data-llen='2085:2108'>外傳云不肖者精化初具而生氣感動觸情縱欲反施</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l97' data-llen='2108:2134'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0052', 'WYG', '001-6a' );" name="001-6a" class="pb">[001-6a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l98' data-llen='2134:2157'>化是以年夀亟夭而性不得長也此生命之㫖耳主臣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l99' data-llen='2157:2180'>謹奉教陟岵陟屺陟岡雖變文就韻抑各有㫖岵者怙</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l100' data-llen='2180:2203'>也屺者恃也岡者况也小弁詩無父何怙無母何恃白</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l101' data-llen='2203:2218'>虎通曰兄者况也以况父法主臣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l102' data-llen='2218:2241'>謹奉教葛之覃兮施于中谷與南有喬木不可休息起</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l103' data-llen='2241:2264'>並無韻此不可明既見豐氏石經本中谷是中逵與萋</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l104' data-llen='2264:2287'>飛合雖此本不足據要此當近理也若不可休息韓詩</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l105' data-llen='2287:2310'>外傳本作休思孔氏正義亦云息字是思字之誤則思</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l106' data-llen='2310:2336'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0052', 'WYG', '001-6b' );" name="001-6b" class="pb">[001-6b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l107' data-llen='2336:2359'>字原是語辭休與求合毛詩本誤也凡詩要無二句無</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l108' data-llen='2359:2382'>韻者况葛覃祇二句猶可若南有喬木將至四句無韻</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l109' data-llen='2382:2390'>矣豈可邪主臣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l110' data-llen='2390:2413'>謹奉教維參與昴昴讀作留此是正音詎押也毛傳云</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l111' data-llen='2413:2436'>昴留也史記律書云北至于留索隠云留即昴也又小</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l112' data-llen='2436:2459'>雅露彼菅茅與之子不猶同韻魯頌薄采其茆與在泮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l113' data-llen='2459:2482'>飲酒同韻則茅亦音留矣又說文音茆為柳而尚書昧</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l114' data-llen='2482:2505'>谷周禮註作柳榖以昧與茅為轉音故亦作柳然則茅</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l115' data-llen='2505:2531'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0052', 'WYG', '001-7a' );" name="001-7a" class="pb">[001-7a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l116' data-llen='2531:2554'>之同音與柳之轉音且爾爾豈况本音乎故曰昴留也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l117' data-llen='2554:2577'>若律書云留言陽氣稽留則不特有其音且有其義矣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l118' data-llen='2577:2585'>故曰留也主臣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l119' data-llen='2585:2608'>謹奉教衞兼邶鄘未悟起自何時漢志書序等皆曰武</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l120' data-llen='2608:2631'>王封武庚于殷命三叔監之而三分其地武王崩三監</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l121' data-llen='2631:2654'>畔周公誅之畢以其地封康叔此誤以三監為武王封</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l122' data-llen='2654:2677'>康叔為成王封故耳按書云孟侯朕其弟則封康者亦</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l123' data-llen='2677:2699'>武也邶鄘未必是三監且衛始封時亦安得即兼邶</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l124' data-llen='2699:2725'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0052', 'WYG', '001-7b' );" name="001-7b" class="pb">[001-7b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l125' data-llen='2725:2748'>鄘有之又書曰明大命于妹邦姝邦紂都也而正義云</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l126' data-llen='2748:2771'>於地屬鄘此統思實康叔為成王所封是時當必盡得</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l127' data-llen='2771:2794'>有邶鄘之地且以桑中詩有沬鄉句屬鄘風故云然不</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l128' data-llen='2794:2817'>知妹邦即朝歌在淇東黎陽之間本衞邑而欲屬之鄘</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l129' data-llen='2817:2840'>則不特衞之兼邶鄘不得明即衞之自為衞亦不得明</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l130' data-llen='2840:2863'>也要是有衞詩時則己兼邶鄘康叔始封時不得兼邶</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l131' data-llen='2863:2871'>鄘此得之主臣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l132' data-llen='2871:2894'>謹奉教衞既兼邶鄘然又稱邶鄘是底解或曰邶鄘之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l133' data-llen='2894:2920'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0052', 'WYG', '001-8a' );" name="001-8a" class="pb">[001-8a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l134' data-llen='2920:2943'>音異於衞音故分繫之信然則莊姜共姜諸詩通作自</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l135' data-llen='2943:2966'>衞宫者安見其一為邶音一為鄘音耳且邶鄘既入衞</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l136' data-llen='2966:2989'>則當通曰衞音齊音敖辟詎仍曰爽鳩之音陳音好巫</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l137' data-llen='2989:3012'>詎仍曰大皥之音此易知也假云作之邶鄘地者為邶</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l138' data-llen='3012:3035'>鄘作之衞地者為衞則漕邑鄘地而邶曰土國城漕泉</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l139' data-llen='3035:3058'>水衞地也而邶曰毖彼泉水又何也或又謂繫其國名</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l140' data-llen='3058:3081'>是太史書法猶春秋楚既滅陳復書陳災糓梁子所謂</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l141' data-llen='3081:3104'>存陳者則齊秦所并不一將奚書之且太史採詩其職</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l142' data-llen='3104:3130'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0052', 'WYG', '001-8b' );" name="001-8b" class="pb">[001-8b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l143' data-llen='3130:3153'>不過輯民風審善敗耳詎事書法即有書法亦偶一見</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l144' data-llen='3153:3176'>之詎必魏唐鄭檜畢情如是走臆邶鄘諸名即樂部名</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l145' data-llen='3176:3199'>也周初列國不一採詩者各判其國詩授之樂官則樂</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l146' data-llen='3199:3222'>官必預班國名考按樂部然後以列國詩分入之雖列</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l147' data-llen='3222:3245'>國代有興絶其樂部班名若故也後比遇詩多者浸假</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l148' data-llen='3245:3268'>于本部過繁仍得入之其國所兼之舊部此但因之作</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l149' data-llen='3268:3291'>標識耳故無深㫖也故周公東山諸詩無可繫即繫之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l150' data-llen='3291:3314'>曰豳以樂部舊有豳名今偶無詩遂實之如樂記曰商</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l151' data-llen='3314:3340'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0052', 'WYG', '001-9a' );" name="001-9a" class="pb">[001-9a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l152' data-llen='3340:3363'>者五帝之遺聲也商人識之故謂之商齊者三代之遺</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l153' data-llen='3363:3386'>聲也齊人識之故謂之齊其曰識正以當時故有商齊</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l154' data-llen='3386:3409'>遺聲而其後之為商齊者取識焉此之謂識識者記也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l155' data-llen='3409:3432'>謂記其名也觀此則邶鄘可曉矣或曰晉本無詩何必</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l156' data-llen='3432:3455'>分繫之唐魏則詩之存没不可考已多矣有晉無晉在</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l157' data-llen='3455:3466'>今詩何足以知之主臣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l158' data-llen='3466:3489'>謹奉教願言則嚏嚏即鼽嚏故鄭箋云嚏當是不敢嚏</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l159' data-llen='3489:3512'>咳之嚏今俗人嚏曰人道我是也獨毛傳云嚏跲也跲</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l160' data-llen='3512:3538'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0052', 'WYG', '001-9b' );" name="001-9b" class="pb">[001-9b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l161' data-llen='3538:3561'>即㰦字玉篇云㰦欠張口也即呵欠耳故孫毓疏云欠</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l162' data-llen='3561:3584'>欠㰦㰦而王肅解詩云願以母道往加之則嚏刼而不</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l163' data-llen='3584:3607'>行此誤㰦為刼而因以跲為躓跲之跲遂致蘇子由解</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l164' data-llen='3607:3630'>亦云願往從之則若有跲制之者讀古之易訛比如此</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l165' data-llen='3630:3634'>主臣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l166' data-llen='3634:3657'>謹奉教我心則說說原有脫音㫖亦從脫見埤雅按之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l167' data-llen='3657:3680'>則以降者忡忡之反脫者惙惙之反忡忡者中而不下</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l168' data-llen='3680:3703'>也故降下之惙惙者綴而不解也故解脫之瞻卬詩彼</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l169' data-llen='3703:3730'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0052', 'WYG', '001-10a' );" name="001-10a" class="pb">[001-10a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l170' data-llen='3730:3744'>宜有罪女覆說之亦作脫主臣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l171' data-llen='3744:3767'>謹奉教爾雅云以衣涉水曰厲謂衣褌入水也又云自</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l172' data-llen='3767:3790'>膝以下為揭自帶以上為厲是底義按之似言水淺及</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l173' data-llen='3790:3813'>膝可揭衣以涉是為自膝以下假水深及帶則需衣褌</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l174' data-llen='3813:3836'>入水矣然帶以上若故故曰自帶以上以此推之似厲</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l175' data-llen='3836:3860'>以帶為節故有時帶亦稱厲方言厲謂之帶孔雅帶之垂</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l176' data-llen='3860:3883'>者為厲都人士詩垂帶而厲此著也有時水碕及帶亦</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l177' data-llen='3883:3906'>稱厲衞詩有狐綏綏在彼淇厲此著也若衣褌入水介</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l178' data-llen='3906:3933'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0052', 'WYG', '001-10b' );" name="001-10b" class="pb">[001-10b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l179' data-llen='3933:3948'>自帶上亦稱厲深則厲著也主臣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l180' data-llen='3948:3971'>謹奉教匏有苦葉匏是瓠八月斷壺壺亦是瓠獨埤雅</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l181' data-llen='3971:3994'>謂三物有分嘗見齊民要術四時類要諸載通云是一</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l182' data-llen='3994:4017'>物繹其說似物種本一區植法異遂有大小圓窳之别</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l183' data-llen='4017:4040'>不必圓者壺長者瓠矣即以涉水一節較之三物正同</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l184' data-llen='4040:4063'>鶡冠子曰中流失船一壺千金左傳曰苦匏不材于人</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l185' data-llen='4063:4086'>供濟而已莊子曰人有五石之瓠何不慮以為大樽而</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l186' data-llen='4086:4094'>浮于江湖主臣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l187' data-llen='4094:4121'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0052', 'WYG', '001-11a' );" name="001-11a" class="pb">[001-11a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l188' data-llen='4121:4144'>謹奉教衞有頓丘三其一名五軍謂魏置五軍于丘傍</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l189' data-llen='4144:4167'>故也在淇水南水經註所謂淇水逕頓丘北者其一名</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l190' data-llen='4167:4190'>五觀在淇上宿胥口蘇代所謂决宿胥之瀆魏無虚頓</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l191' data-llen='4190:4220'>丘者其一名帝丘帝頓聲轉亦近淇春秋所謂衛<img height='20' width='20' alt='&amp;KR1971' title='KR1971' src='https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR1971.png'/>于</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l192' data-llen='4220:4243'>帝丘帝王世紀所謂顓頊塟帝丘城者凡此三頓丘鄉</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l193' data-llen='4243:4266'>未審至於頓丘是何地今按之皆在淇上似但涉淇皆</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l194' data-llen='4266:4273'>可至者主臣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l195' data-llen='4273:4296'>謹奉教溱洧二水而合流於鄭溱水出鄶城西北經鄶</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l196' data-llen='4296:4323'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0052', 'WYG', '001-11b' );" name="001-11b" class="pb">[001-11b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l197' data-llen='4323:4346'>城入洧洧水出陽城山與溱水合然後同自西北入新</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l198' data-llen='4346:4369'>鄭城迤邐入潁則溱洧雖二水而已合為一矣故前可</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l199' data-llen='4369:4387'>並稱曰溱與洧其下即可曰洧之水主臣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l200' data-llen='4387:4410'>謹奉教周禮籥章氏祈年于田祖則吹豳雅蜡祭則吹</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l201' data-llen='4410:4433'>豳頌有為楚茨大田甫田諸詩是豳雅噫嘻載芟豐年</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l202' data-llen='4433:4456'>諸詩是豳頌有為不然豳風中自有雅自有頌以豳風</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l203' data-llen='4456:4479'>一詩三分而得之又有為豳别有雅頌今已亡又有為</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l204' data-llen='4479:4503'>即豳風一詩吹之則其調通可為雅通可為頌諸說不同</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l205' data-llen='4503:4530'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0052', 'WYG', '001-12a' );" name="001-12a" class="pb">[001-12a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l206' data-llen='4530:4553'>但後說近是此何故風雅頌祗樂調區名如西洲呉聲</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l207' data-llen='4553:4576'>等祗以聲不以辭故緜蠻黍離辭調亦似而緜蠻自為</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l208' data-llen='4576:4599'>雅黍離自為風樂調與詩調判然不屬此甚著者比以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l209' data-llen='4599:4622'>大戴禮投壺篇質之其云凡雅十六篇八篇可歌歌鹿</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l210' data-llen='4622:4645'>鳴貍首鵲巢采繁采蘋伐檀白駒騶虞今按之但鹿鳴</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l211' data-llen='4645:4668'>白駒在小雅貍首今已亡餘俱國風耳謂之雅者正以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l212' data-llen='4668:4691'>雅調歌之可為雅故矣又漢杜䕫傳云舊雅凡四曲一</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l213' data-llen='4691:4714'>鹿鳴二騶虞三伐檀四文王今伐檀騶虞皆風詩主臣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l214' data-llen='4714:4741'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0052', 'WYG', '001-12b' );" name="001-12b" class="pb">[001-12b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l215' data-llen='4741:4764'>謹奉教燕禮有房中樂即二南矣秦名夀人漢名安世</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l216' data-llen='4764:4787'>樂又名楚調由高帝好楚聲耳今樂府相和歌詞有清</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l217' data-llen='4787:4810'>商三調晉荀朂所定而唐禮樂志又云平調清調瑟調</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l218' data-llen='4810:4833'>皆周房中遺聲也漢世謂之三調又名楚調則臆房中</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l219' data-llen='4833:4856'>樂亦但取律調相尋不拘拘詞句故當時猶有襲周時</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l220' data-llen='4856:4879'>遺聲而逓變者如漢相和歌詞故非四言唐李白清平</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l221' data-llen='4879:4902'>調詞且用絶句三并非相和歌詞可例也昔劉迅嘗取</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l222' data-llen='4902:4925'>房中歌至後庭鬬百草臨春樂小年子之類以當雅章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l223' data-llen='4925:4952'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0052', 'WYG', '001-13a' );" name="001-13a" class="pb">[001-13a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l224' data-llen='4952:4976'>又取巴渝舞折楊柳白頭吟之類以當國風臆當時猶能</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l225' data-llen='4976:4999'>彷彿古今聲音敢為傅㑹耳後人讀詩者不解審聲但</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l226' data-llen='4999:5022'>强取詩義已不知樂又鄙者謂詩句單複短長皆有成</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l227' data-llen='5022:5041'>數則是以詞曲當古樂其舛不待辨耳主臣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l228' data-llen='5041:5064'>謹奉教無田甫田田字應狄因翻與無思逺人人字隔</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l229' data-llen='5064:5087'>合此與兎罝桑柔野有死麕何彼穠矣諸詩同集傳失</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l230' data-llen='5087:5092'>之主臣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l231' data-llen='5092:5115'>謹奉教鄭詩秉蕳有作秉菅有作秉蘭陸氏釋文云蕳</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l232' data-llen='5115:5142'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0052', 'WYG', '001-13b' );" name="001-13b" class="pb">[001-13b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l233' data-llen='5142:5165'>字從草韓詩云蓮也若作竹下是簡策之簡則當時又</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l234' data-llen='5165:5188'>有從竹下者矣但韓詩作蓮則贈芍藥時無蓮耳主臣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l235' data-llen='5188:5211'>謹奉教知子之來之雜珮以贈之舊訓是對客語以上</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l236' data-llen='5211:5234'>章既酒食笙瑟燕賓客矣至是又對客曰早知子來當</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l237' data-llen='5234:5257'>預備雜珮以贈子惜今不及也歐陽子與郭秀才書中</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l238' data-llen='5257:5280'>有云獨為秀才賦詩女曰鷄鳴之卒章曰知子之來之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l239' data-llen='5280:5303'>雜珮以贈之取其知客之來預儲珩璜琚瑀之美以送</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l240' data-llen='5303:5323'>客雖無此物猶言之以致其意厚也正同主臣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l241' data-llen='5323:5350'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0052', 'WYG', '001-14a' );" name="001-14a" class="pb">[001-14a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l242' data-llen='5350:5373'>謹奉教不念昔者伊予來塈鄭箋云不念往昔我始來</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l243' data-llen='5373:5396'>之時安息我也北魏王肅妻謝氏寄肅詩云本為簿上</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l244' data-llen='5396:5418'>蠶今作機上絲得路逐勝去頗憶纒綿時正同王臣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l245' data-llen='5418:5441'>謹奉教焉得諼草諼忘也但言善忘耳初不定云忘憂</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l246' data-llen='5441:5464'>自後人以諼草為萱草遂起萱草忘憂之說走比作是</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l247' data-llen='5464:5487'>語人惑之既讀陸機贈從兄車騎詩有云焉得忘歸草</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l248' data-llen='5487:5510'>言樹背與衿則且易忘憂為忘歸矣陸本思歸者故云</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l249' data-llen='5510:5533'>忘歸則此本思不歸者詎不可忘不歸耶忘是虚字不</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l250' data-llen='5533:5560'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0052', 'WYG', '001-14b' );" name="001-14b" class="pb">[001-14b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l251' data-llen='5560:5583'>必定歸亦何必定憂因解古人讀書較今通達比然也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l252' data-llen='5583:5587'>主臣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l253' data-llen='5587:5610'>謹奉教月出之光當作日字此字形之誤此見印古詩</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l254' data-llen='5610:5633'>話若曰不趐鷄鳴已逮旦蒼蠅有聲矣因蒼蠅聲不先</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l255' data-llen='5633:5656'>于鷄聲故然也又曰不趐逮旦日已出有光矣因月光</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l256' data-llen='5656:5679'>不嘗先鄉明故然也此是也但又有不更日字而亦不</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l257' data-llen='5679:5700'>礙于蠅不先聲月不嘗夜之㫖見國風省篇主臣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l258' data-llen='5700:5723'>謹奉教四月秀葽夏小正四月有秀幽幽葽聲轉耳鄭</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l259' data-llen='5723:5750'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0052', 'WYG', '001-15a' );" name="001-15a" class="pb">[001-15a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l260' data-llen='5750:5773'>箋據夏小正妄以王萯為葽按王萯即吕覽中所謂王</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l261' data-llen='5773:5797'>善月令中所謂王𤓰者葽即吕覽中所謂苦菜者苦菜</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l262' data-llen='5797:5821'>秀即秀葽也以苦菜秀為王𤓰生可乎又按苦菜名葽</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l263' data-llen='5821:5844'>然亦名逺志亦名細草故逸周書時訓解云小滿之日</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l264' data-llen='5844:5867'>苦菜秀苦菜不秀賢人潛伏而晉郝隆譏謝東山亦云</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l265' data-llen='5867:5890'>處為逺志出為小草以苦菜萌為細草故苦菜秀則發</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l266' data-llen='5890:5913'>為細草所謂出為小草根為逺志故苦菜不秀則藏為</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l267' data-llen='5913:5936'>逺志所謂處為逺志亦所謂賢人潛伏也郝隆語正本</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l268' data-llen='5936:5963'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0052', 'WYG', '001-15b' );" name="001-15b" class="pb">[001-15b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l269' data-llen='5963:5971'>時訓解耳主臣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l270' data-llen='5971:5994'>謹奉教詩國風所第不同故歐陽子詩譜補亡後序有</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l271' data-llen='5994:6017'>云周南召南弼鄘衞王鄭齊豳秦魏唐陳檜曹此孔子</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l272' data-llen='6017:6040'>未删詩前太師樂歌所第也周召弼鄘衞王檜鄭齊魏</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l273' data-llen='6040:6063'>唐秦陳曹豳此鄭氏詩譜所第也斥檜後陳此今詩所</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l274' data-llen='6063:6086'>第也但按左傳襄二十九年季札觀樂歌齊之後即歌</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l275' data-llen='6086:6109'>豳然即歌魏此太師所第與歐陽所云稍異若鄭譜所</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l276' data-llen='6109:6132'>第則與今詩所傳無别正義云鄭譜王在豳後者退就</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l277' data-llen='6132:6159'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0052', 'WYG', '001-16a' );" name="001-16a" class="pb">[001-16a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l278' data-llen='6159:6182'>雅頌并言王世故耳則孔氏鄭譜本與歐陽所云又異</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l279' data-llen='6182:6200'>然又與今本鄭譜各不同不悟何也主臣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l280' data-llen='6200:6223'>謹奉教比興賦詩中義耳昔張逸問鄭小同何詩近于</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l281' data-llen='6223:6246'>比興賦答曰比興賦呉札觀樂時已不歌也此誤解太</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l282' data-llen='6246:6269'>師六詩之説以風雅頌比興賦通是詩故曰呉札時已</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l283' data-llen='6269:6292'>不歌言呉札時此三詩已亡耳從來比興賦不悟如此</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l284' data-llen='6292:6296'>主臣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l285' data-llen='6296:6319'>謹奉教雅者正也雅字古文原作正字亦即正㫖初無</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l286' data-llen='6319:6346'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0052', 'WYG', '001-16b' );" name="001-16b" class="pb">[001-16b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l287' data-llen='6346:6369'>正雅之說若既雅又正是雅雅矣後人不悟雅是正字</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l288' data-llen='6369:6392'>以為是雅也而文或以正則此必正雅也既有正雅則</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l289' data-llen='6392:6415'>必有變雅既有正雅變雅則必又有正風變風正變之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l290' data-llen='6415:6437'>説此所由滋矣要其始由不識雅字耳頌者容也從</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l291' data-llen='6437:6460'>頁頁首也故作容頌即容字故先儒引漢書徐生善容</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l292' data-llen='6460:6483'>呉王濞傳他國郡吏來捕亡者頌共禁不與為騐假曰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l293' data-llen='6483:6506'>形容以頌之頌其德容仍是頌頌也且如孔疏引太師</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l294' data-llen='6506:6530'>註云誦今之徳廣以美之鄭譜云頌之言容天子之德光</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l295' data-llen='6530:6557'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0052', 'WYG', '001-17a' );" name="001-17a" class="pb">[001-17a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l296' data-llen='6557:6580'>被四表格于上下無不持載無不覆幬此之謂容則是</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l297' data-llen='6580:6603'>以容為有容之容固屬别㫖至若以形為容亦宜云容</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l298' data-llen='6603:6626'>先王之功德容先王之情状而大序云美盛德之形容</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l299' data-llen='6626:6647'>正義云述祭祀之情狀猶似不畢悟頌字者主臣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l300' data-llen='6647:6670'>謹奉教風雅無正變立于文武之朝不得不誦文武時</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l301' data-llen='6670:6693'>耳生乎幽平之世不能不刺幽平勢耳設以時升降便</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l302' data-llen='6693:6716'>題正變是並不判詩體徒以文之頌美風刺作别識也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l303' data-llen='6716:6739'>則必典謨為正書誓誥為變書矣或曰樂聲有正變如</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l304' data-llen='6739:6766'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0052', 'WYG', '001-17b' );" name="001-17b" class="pb">[001-17b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l305' data-llen='6766:6789'>樂記曰正聲感人而和氣應之又曰聲相應故生變此</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l306' data-llen='6789:6812'>是正變但變不與正對變是清濁輕重不同耳與姦聲</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l307' data-llen='6812:6835'>犯正有辨此如子夜有變歌歡聞有變曲特是變換無</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l308' data-llen='6835:6858'>與升降故但可曰詩有貞淫樂有邪正此為得之主臣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l309' data-llen='6858:6881'>謹奉教鹿鳴燕嘉賓羣臣謂四方之賓本國之臣也但</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l310' data-llen='6881:6904'>燕有四等一是諸侯無事一是卿大夫有王事之勞一</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l311' data-llen='6904:6927'>是卿大夫聘而來還一是四方來聘之客凡燕禮不出</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l312' data-llen='6927:6933'>四者主臣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l313' data-llen='6933:6960'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0052', 'WYG', '001-18a' );" name="001-18a" class="pb">[001-18a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l314' data-llen='6960:6983'>謹奉教王命南仲不悟是何南仲故此詩亦不辨為何</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l315' data-llen='6983:7006'>王時詩按漢書古今人表有南中中即仲也在厲王時</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l316' data-llen='7006:7029'>但匃奴傳又云出車彭彭城彼朔方宣王命將征伐玁</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l317' data-llen='7029:7052'>狁故詩人美大其功則又當在宣王時矣詎仲本厲王</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l318' data-llen='7052:7075'>時人而宣王命將時尚在邪然大雅常武詩此宣王時</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l319' data-llen='7075:7098'>詩也中有云王命卿士南仲太祖則此時南仲已為太</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l320' data-llen='7098:7121'>師皇父之始祖矣其必非厲宣時又甚著者考竹書殷</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l321' data-llen='7121:7144'>帝乙三年王命南仲西拒昆夷城朔方又後漢龎參傳</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l322' data-llen='7144:7171'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0052', 'WYG', '001-18b' );" name="001-18b" class="pb">[001-18b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l323' data-llen='7171:7194'>有云是以赫赫南仲列在周詩據二書所云或在殷或</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l324' data-llen='7194:7217'>在周要只當在王季專鈇鉞曁文王為西伯時始得不</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l325' data-llen='7217:7240'>然鹿鳴二十二篇畢周初詩也而獨以此詩為厲宣時</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l326' data-llen='7240:7263'>詎有是矣若漢書一為厲王一為宣王而史記匃奴傳</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l327' data-llen='7263:7286'>又云在襄王時又云在懿王時即一漢史其自為矛盾</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l328' data-llen='7286:7301'>若此古文之難信又比然者主臣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l329' data-llen='7301:7324'>謹奉教春秋記魯夫人失于魯皆為魯事今刺之者獨</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l330' data-llen='7324:7347'>在齊故知婁豬之歌必聞自宋也氓詩云士之躭兮猶</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l331' data-llen='7347:7374'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0052', 'WYG', '001-19a' );" name="001-19a" class="pb">[001-19a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l332' data-llen='7374:7397'>可說也女之躭兮不可説也故知說亦是稱說之說主</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l333' data-llen='7397:7400'>臣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l334' data-llen='7400:7423'>謹奉教凡有所聞則法之有所諫則納之不聞而比若</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l335' data-llen='7423:7446'>有所法不諫而比若有所納虚之至也故曰不聞亦式</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l336' data-llen='7446:7454'>不諫亦入主臣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l337' data-llen='7454:7477'>謹奉教皇矣篇居岐之陽文王遷程矣魯頌居岐之陽</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l338' data-llen='7477:7500'>太王遷岐矣但皆為岐陽耳地理志太王邑在扶風美</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l339' data-llen='7500:7518'>陽縣文王邑在扶風安陵縣皆岐南主臣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l340' data-llen='7518:7545'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0052', 'WYG', '001-19b' );" name="001-19b" class="pb">[001-19b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l341' data-llen='7545:7568'>謹奉教束晢補亡宋人比訿之以詩本無辭不必補也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l342' data-llen='7568:7591'>但先時早有補亡者曾不始束觀夏侯有補周詩其序</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l343' data-llen='7591:7614'>曰周詩者南陔白華華黍田庚崇丘由儀六篇有其㫖</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l344' data-llen='7614:7637'>而亡其辭湛續其亡則是湛已先補之矣今所傳特束</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l345' data-llen='7637:7643'>詩耳王臣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l346' data-llen='7643:7646'>　</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l347' data-llen='7646:7649'>　</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l348' data-llen='7649:7656'>　詩札卷一</span><br/>
</p>
